6.title: Breaking Archontic Control with David Icke
6.plot: In this episode of Open Minds with Regina Meredith, David Icke explains how we can use the power of love to break free from archontic control.

1.title: Michael Tellinger on Secrets of Lost Civilizations
1.plot: Michael Tellinger, author, scientist, explorer, has become a real-life Indiana Jones, making groundbreaking discoveries about ancient vanished civilizations at the southern tip of Africa.

23.title: Project Pegasus Revealed with Andrew Basiago
23.plot: While many of us struggle with the complexities of ordinary consciousness, other people naturally have the ability to see beyond the limits of time and space. Andrew Basiago became aware of these abilities at a very young age and was tapped for military use. Now, he reveals the secret programs that he was once a part of, with Project Pegasus in this interview with Regina Meredith originally webcast December 3, 2013. Andrew D. 30.title: Technology and Consciousness with Adam Curry
30.plot: What the future holds for us is uncertain. But we can expect a world filled with technology advancing at an ever-quickening pace. With such a future, is there any place for the human mind? Perhaps technology can provide a solution to advance human consciousness beyond any technological limitation. Adam Curry explains the coming intersection of technology and consciousness in this interview with Regina Meredith originally webcast June 30, 2015. Adam M. 8.title: Disclosing Government Disinformation with Paul Hellyer
8.plot: Join Regina Meredith and Paola Harris in this new episode of Open Minds. What we learn, is not only are we not alone, but there is a means by which we can initiate contact with these otherworldly beings.

14.title: From Folklore to Fact: Bigfoot & Dog Man with Jack Cary
14.plot: Join Regina Meredith and Jack Cary in this new episode of Open Minds. He has been hot on the trail of cryptozoological wonders like Bigfoot and Dog Man.

1.title: Living the Blue Avian's Message with Corey Goode
1.plot: Join Regina Meredith and Corey Goode in this new episode of Open Minds. As they discuss the importance of the message from the Blue Sphere Being Alliance.

13.title: Traversing Parallel Realities with Jason Quitt
13.plot: Join Regina Meredith and Dr. Bradley Nelson in this new episode of Open Minds. His insights can help you successfully and safely traverse previously unfathomable realms of existence.

10.title: Photographic Evidence of Alien Encounters with Paola Harris
10.plot: Join Regina Meredith in this episode of Open Minds as Paola Harris shares photographs from cases involving encounters with extraterrestrial beings.

imdb.plot outline: Host Regina Meredith conducts interviews with thought-provoking luminaries, cutting-edge visionaries and tireless researchers, providing crucial information to awaken viewers to new perspectives that spark awareness, understanding and ultimately, transformation.
